      "content": "```markdown\n## GET /user\n\nRetrieves the profile information for the authenticated user, providing granular access to user metadata. This endpoint mandates valid authentication credentials for secure data retrieval.\n\n**Request Details:**\n*   **Method:** `GET`\n*   **Path:** `/user`\n*   **Authentication Scheme:** Bearer Token required in the `Authorization` header.\n\n**Request Parameters:**\nNone are accepted for this read-only operation.\n\n**Response Structure (200 OK):**\nA JSON object detailing the user profile.\n\n**Response Body Fields:**\n*   `user_id`: (String) Unique identifier for the user.\n*   `username`: (String) The user's chosen display name.\n*   `email_address`: (String) The primary contact email.\n*   `account_status`: (Enum) Current status (e.g., ACTIVE, SUSPENDED).\n*   `creation_timestamp`: (DateTime) When the account was provisioned.\n*   `last_login`: (DateTime) Timestamp of the most recent successful login.\n\n**Response Headers:**\n`Content-Type`: `application/json`\n`X-",
